ingredients.ingredient: 1 (12 ounce) bag DOLE® All Natural Southwest Salad Kit
1 cup fresh salsa, drained of excess juice
⅔ cup additional shredded Cheddar cheese
¼ cup sliced black olives, well drained

cookingTips: Bake tortillas in a muffin tin at 375°F for 10-12 minutes to create crispy cups
Drain salsa through a fine mesh strainer to prevent soggy taco cups
Assemble taco cups just before serving to maintain crispy tortilla texture
enrichment.coachingPrompt: Would you make homemade taco cups from corn tortillas or use store-bought crispy shells for convenience?
